Class BackToStartAction

java.lang.Object
model.entity.BackToStartAction
All Implemented Interfaces:
TileAction
public class BackToStartAction extends Object implements TileAction
This class represents an action that sends a player back to a specified tile on the board. It implements the TileAction interface.
